overview: Enter the mysterious world of renowned magician Samantha Crane (Julia Ann) ... where everything-and-nothing-is as it seems! Once heralded as America's top female magician, Samantha's voracious sexual appetite and uninhibited eroticism made her a prime target for the tabloids. Now hidden away in her mansion, Samantha agrees to share her story with reporter Jack Reynolds (Julian). But is it the truth ... or simply more sleight of hand?
title: Sex Magician
